Maintainer: Nima Hejazi <nh@nimahejazi.org>
Description: Estimators of a parameter arising in the decomposition of the
    population intervention causal effect of stochastic interventions under
    mediation analysis, including one-step augmented inverse probability
    weighted (AIPW), re-weighting (IPW), and substitution estimators. This
    parameter constitutes one of two parts of the population intervention
    (in)direct effect in the mediation setting with stochastic interventions,
    thus these estimators may be used in constructing assessing the (in)direct
    effect under stochastic treatment regimes, including incremental propensity
    score interventions and standard location shifts of the intervention (Díaz
    and Hejazi; 2019 (submitted); <https://arxiv.org/abs/1901.02776>).
